Px48A2YgNj6THfMWfsPidqU6zBVB87JGhEksbwq_0g&oe=671E335B"}, {"file_name": "G_SS_e.png", "id": "551243527231744", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982477_551243530565077_3068936903857039782_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=8aZr9D7H6uwQ7kNvgHwdxsw&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDvgKxYnrvAOileeVc3b0exiMbPTxtP5HAfvi6ywiX_7Q&oe=671E3443"}, {"file_name": "G_SS_c.png", "id": "1062477815230090", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982571_1062477818563423_3356252898534236255_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=uKsB37AlkuQQ7kNvgHFlJQW&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC05bZavfIfOlRkiLxZsPs3o_BF4KQ07Mh2CKQEiRj90w&oe=671E33FB"}, {"file_name": "GolfNewAndamanSS_f.png", "id": "3388250831482372", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75393561_3388250838149038_2779458500181265324_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=26InHn8dReoQ7kNvgHNi_Gb&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCWHXGf69OcisHE2aYTQjoikhfgxbRtbzHb-7RFOjVekg&oe=671E1EA1"}, {"file_name": "G_SS_b.png", "id": "1905120206665961", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982524_1905120209999294_3848564138150346797_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=eDHFYxp5k0MQ7kNvgHOR30k&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA_iYr8J97G8BEKfrq3wbtpKGVmrYCI2yYdwZHSTeDdAw&oe=671E138D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "GolfPosterA_2560x1440.png", "id": "359996137196788", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035458_359996140530121_3677596953659391473_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qJcVa376GGAQ7kNvgEctajA&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAFqyRtnDCtMhdRrbwambvBwhlcztjmrJYKvtiZHC0rvg&oe=671E1E3A"}, "display_name": "Beyond Putt : Upgrades Home.  Mixed Reality - Mini Golf", "keywords": ["Golf", "Family", "Casual", "Mini", "puzzle"], "long_description": "# Beyond Putt and the Future of Mixed Reality\n\nStep into a whole new dimension with Beyond Putt, where cutting-edge Mixed Reality (MR) tech turns your living room into an epic mini-golf course. **The game adapts to your space**, creating a dynamic setup that evolves based on your surroundings. With our advanced physics engine, **every collision\u2014whether it's with the ball or even scanned furniture**\u2014feels incredibly real. Watch as the ball reacts to obstacles in your space, adding a new layer of immersion and strategy that takes your game to the next level. \n\nAnd if you're ready for a deeper dive, our Virtual Reality (VR) mode transports you to jaw-dropping courses that look and feel like the real deal. With ultra-realistic graphics and gameplay, you'll find yourself exploring meticulously crafted environments where every putt feels like you're on a pro mini-golf course. Navigate everything from peaceful gardens to futuristic terrains, all designed to keep you hooked and elevate your play. \n", "short_description": "\"Beyond Putt  in Mixed Reality\" is an immersive gaming experience that combines the fun and excitement of traditional mini golf with cutting-edge Mixed reality technology. Players can step into a virtual course set in your own home, interact with virtual obstacles and challenges, and compete against friends through Leaderboard. With realistic physics and stunning visuals, Beyond Putt in Mixed Reality offers a unique and engaging twist on a classic game\n"}]}, "developer_name": "Biswa Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://biswagames.com/privacy_policy/beyondputt/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Biswa Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.biswagames.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUI