", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035336_308307238828069_3481913805081268237_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=14myV8bIEbkQ7kNvgE9Kemx&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAR1g_XI7ugSupuzbW4j3IgU_RkVJkup4IIECBnKIQiOQ&oe=671E2CD7"}]}, "id": "355207117536593", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "GolfSS_5.png", "id": "7798354186864660", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984472_7798354190197993_6671377659150079514_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=t4j54oCDXqgQ7kNvgGQGN1l&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC_tp77dDOhT05Sm_2FgFu9wWll9Hy_Ci0QH5NIITb58w&oe=671E2798"}, {"file_name": "GolfSS_2b.png", "id": "1201426934161353", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982665_1201426937494686_4901747546808758779_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=2Eao-0m5C_MQ7kNvgGM4nyz&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCu9ExongwcyMtHJX5QFuTO0-f2s0AslDc7a3laKy7iQA&oe=671E261F"}, {"file_name": "GolfSS_5b.png", "id": "1532102834319644", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75395593_1532102837652977_2116554826464113881_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=tzf1_2uHMpoQ7kNvgHkQgl-&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCZPMQoSVu7-pfw36njksZdbiRdhLkzz3MVYuwKN5wBBA&oe=671E1B07"}, {"file_name": "GolfSS_4.png", "id": "447547417789522", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035470_447547421122855_100407660325312671_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=87hGEnZLUZIQ7kNvgHLWv7p&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD3ulefEMHzZWawUAQNXijKuI11v4oYE_wlV5GKmI2Xpg&oe=671E3630"}, {"file_name": "GolfSS_1.png", "id": "3798629260373195", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75207239_3798629267039861_1404983112144480687_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=y3yqciWRatQQ7kNvgHLwbl7&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBHUmtwuep1VUR1357n9yLaNCJxrZJQvRJoQ4vKruzL2g&oe=671E3DA4"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Beyond Putt:  Mini Golf", "keywords": [], "long_description": "\"Beyond Putt  in Mixed Reality\" is an innovative and captivating gaming experience that transports players into a world where the boundaries between reality and virtuality blur. This cutting-edge game combines the beloved pastime of mini golf with the immersive capabilities of mixed reality technology, creating an engaging and unforgettable adventure for players.\n\nOne of the most remarkable features of \"Beyond Putt in Mixed Reality\" is its realistic physics engine, which accurately simulates the behavior of the ball and the environment. This attention to detail enhances the authenticity of the gameplay, allowing you to experience the thrill of sinking a challenging putt or navigating a tricky obstacle with precision and finesse.\n\nWith its seamless integration of virtual elements into the real world, \"Beyond Putt in Mixed Reality\" provides an immersive and interactive gaming experience like no other. It not only entertains and delights players but also sparks their imagination and sense of wonder as they explore fantastical landscapes and conquer exciting challenges. Get ready to embark on a mini golf adventure like never before in \"Beyond Putt in Mixed Reality\"!", "short_description": "\"Beyond Putt  in Mixed Reality\" is an immersive gaming experience that combines the fun and excitement of traditional mini golf with cutting-edge mixed reality technology. Players can step into a virtual course set in your own home, interact with virtual obstacles and challenges, and compete against friends through Leaderboard. With realistic physics and stunning visuals, Beyond Putt in Mixed Reality offers a unique and engaging twist on a classic game"}]}, "developer_name": "Biswa Games", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://biswagames.com/privacy_policy/beyondputt/", "developer_terms_